NOTE: This is the code used in the experiments for the proceedings version of
the Riposte paper, which appeared at the 2017 IEEE Symposium on Security and
Privacy. 

To fix an error in the AlmostEqual protocol (Section 5.1) pointed out to us by
Elette Boyle, we have slightly changed the checking protocol in an updated
version of the paper. The revised paper is available at
    https://arxiv.org/abs/1503.06115
The protocol change should have a negligible performance impact and we leave
the code used in the proceedings version here for reference.

